AVAILABLE FOR ADOPTION!!! Meet Patches an adorable 1-2 year old Lab/Terrier mix. Patches has an incredibly sweet disposition. She is an easy going girl that loves everyone she meet. Patches was recently rescued from an area shelter and is adjusting wonderfully in her foster home. She is very smart girl that is very eager to please. She already knows commands like sit, stay and lay down. She is good on the leash and is a joy to walk. She is house and crate trained. If you looking for a new addition to your family or just a loyal companion look no further Patches is the girl for you. She is spayed, current on vaccines and microchipped. She currently weighs 45lbs and is full grown. Patches is ready and waiting to meet her forever family. He would be the perfect only cat if you are looking for a solo kitty but could also share space willingly. His loyalty is unwavering and hopes yours will be too. Pounce loves the laser light and of course, any toys with bells or a bit of cat nip.

This lovable, friendly girl is ready to join a family on a lifetime of adventures- come meet her today!
